cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper introduces a new ensemble, deep learning approach for classification, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper specifically discusses the use of deep learning models for image and text classification, which further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
